{"tid":622462,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞] 《最痛中經過》 [原曲：全世界誰傾聽你]","createTime":"2018-04-09T07:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T16:34:30.000Z","uid":108844,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce2644e7a56ecec5c4180aa3d80af3fc3a00c65","tid":622462,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:08:36.000Z","msg":"原曲：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JHhEyaKEwHw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJHhEyaKEwHw&d=zzcAzgRpBJJpPIykeAO1UzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=141ccbb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JHhEyaKEwHw</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n早排碌youtube先聽到哩首歌，聽第一次已經好著迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是就有改哩份詞嘅念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n故事係發生喺一個準備落雨嘅晚上。你同佢分手已經幾個月嘅時間，但你依然好掛住佢。你嚟到以前同佢成日去嘅尖沙嘴海旁，正當你沉醉喺街頭音樂之際，突然間你見到佢......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你有好多嘢想同佢講，好想話佢知你有幾掛住佢。你都感覺到佢見返你好驚喜，但你一諗起佢之前同你相處間嘅摩擦，佢面對爭吵時嘅態度，你甚至懷疑佢只係當你水泡，你好驚佢會再傷害你。習慣食住你嘅佢，又點會唔知你嘅心思，於是佢一啖嘴埋嚟......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n《最痛中經過》<br />\n<br />\n雲灰灰 抑壓著 往日氣燄<br />\n如果可 傾瀉又 哪需友善<br />\n沿海邊歌舞中找救贖<br />\n放慢步伐再懷念<br />\n<br />\n夜空空 風正動 這是美夢<br />\n彈指間 渲染著 你的戲弄<br />\n仍執於跟你再分伯仲<br />\n偶遇又盡見裂縫<br />\n<br />\n從回憶最痛中經過 而塵土飛舞誰跌墮<br />\n風光不再 怎麼相愛<br />\n雖記著 但現實裡 又奈何<br />\n<br />\n夜空空 風正動 這是美夢<br />\n彈指間 渲染著 你的戲弄<br />\n仍急於跟你再分伯仲<br />\n過問 又負了落紅<br />\n<br />\n從回憶最痛中經過 而塵土飛舞誰跌墮<br />\n總想貪更多 得不到你勸阻<br />\n難免 滲透半分怯懦<br />\n而曾經再痛都忍過 彌留間得到誰協助<br />\n風光不再 怎麼相愛<br />\n想軟弱 但望著你 又奈何<br />\n<br />\n沾雨的你不屑於禱告 急切一吻太恐怖<br />\n怕是你認愛但背後磨著刀<br />\n<br />\n從回憶最痛中經過 而塵土飛舞誰跌墮<br />\n表演者太多 偏偏點唱更多<br />\n是你 最愛那首輓歌<br />\n而曾經再痛都忍過 彌留間得到誰協助<br />\n風光不再 怎麼相愛<br />\n想軟弱 但望著你 又奈何<br />\n<br />\n風光不再 怎麼相愛<br />\n想軟弱 但望著你 又奈何"},{"pid":"64486a47c9e8ddf737dd691310697a4299a999bc","tid":622462,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d297dee2c4916babba8c152aacbc5f20a7f37719","tid":622462,"uid":14314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"好鐘意呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打改得幾好"},{"pid":"f4c655dc8de2fd14ac448aa3bf7e90f6917a2477","tid":622462,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d297dee2c4916babba8c152aacbc5f20a7f37719","tid":622462,"uid":14314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"好鐘意呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打改得幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:55:47.000Z","msg":"多謝G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278648093be0497282cd034353832cb5a9fb451a","tid":622462,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34dbee38cab15d638981dd7d468968666549bca9","tid":622462,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"278648093be0497282cd034353832cb5a9fb451a","tid":622462,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T07:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"係善巴啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe88c07196cef2a90a34d4f7b1a296b15884822","tid":622462,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":